□ 撰寫專業論文及表達之能力
 
 

課程概述 Course Description
       本課程首先介紹海岸地區的定義與不同目的多重使用所造成海岸空間與資源衝突的問題，在瞭解海岸管理的必要性後，逐步介紹目前海洋管理主要使用的方法，包括整合性海岸管理、海洋空間規劃、海洋分區等。本課程並介紹及分析台灣海岸管理的體制架構，同時列舉其他國家海岸管理的作法，做為案例探討。This course is to introduce the definition and scope of coastal zones and its inherent problems due to conflicting uses of coastal space and resources. The course will present major management tools to cope with the problem, including integrated coastal zone management, marine spatial planning and ocean zoning. In addition, the management framework of Taiwan and case studies of other countries pertaining to coastal management will be discussed as well.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
介紹海岸管理的內涵與必要性探討台灣目前海岸管理體制與相關法規瞭解國際間主要使用海岸管理的方法，啟發學生在此領域的管理應用或後續研究。 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Definition and scope of coastal zones2Multiple uses of coastal areas3Necessity of coastal management4Integrated coastal zone management5Marine spatial planning6Ocean zoning7Taiwan's coastal issues8Taiwan's coastal management framework9Taiwan's coastal management framework10Countermeasures of coastal erosion11Beach certification12US coastal management framework13Zoning within the GBRMP (Australia)14Zoning in the UK waters and OSPAR15Principles underscoring ocean zoning success16Field study17Field study18Field study 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


